,"kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"It's good to think that way especially in today's time.. people mostly think of themselves and once they feel like there is nothing left they tend to part ways and it hurts bad. It happens..But again it's not the case for everyone..sometimes you end up with good people who genuinely care for you..If there is bad in the world good exists too otherwise the world would be a hopeless sad olace","time":"Dec 08, 2023 11:52 am","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"❤️"}]},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Can I ask something","time":"Dec 08, 2023 11:54 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Yess ma'am","time":"Dec 08, 2023 11:54 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"What are we ?","time":"Dec 08, 2023 11:54 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"I will answer it for me, we are two people who met by coincidence (twice) trying to understand each other, someone who we can talk to and share things, happiness, sorrow and try to be there when in need and hopeful of what the future holds","time":"Dec 08, 2023 11:58 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"That’s diplomatic sir","time":"Dec 08, 2023 11:59 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Sometimes you can't define things in a single word because it doesn't exist","time":"Dec 08, 2023 11:59 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Might be for you, but it's true for me","time":"Dec 08, 2023 12:00 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"It’s diplomatic cause you answered about what we do in this situationship and not exactly what we would call it.","time":"Dec 08, 2023 12:02 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"And I guess we cannot define things cause we see it in a complex view, and WE are complex for you I think","time":"Dec 08, 2023 12:03 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Which doesn’t feel good to realise","time":"Dec 08, 2023 12:03 pm","kind":"msg"},